{"type": "article", "id": 56043, "title": "可 360 度旋转的吊灯，灵感源自月球运行轨迹｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-09-03T22:58:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 52466, "name": "Throwboy"}, {"id": 50827, "name": "Studio 7.5"}, {"id": 52467, "name": "XtreeE"}, {"id": 21587, "name": "Muuto"}, {"id": 52468, "name": "Taku Omura"}, {"id": 52469, "name": "Helen Kontouris"}, {"id": 52470, "name": "Jesse Ede"}, {"id": 21591, "name": "Anderssen & Voll"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 134, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180903193956TtYlzXEVqe95Oo8w.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s4 {font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s5 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s7 {font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} span.s8 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #337ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #337ab7} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Outline Sofa Series by Anderssen &amp; Voll for Muuto</h3><p>丹麦设计品牌 Muuto 推出了其首款高背沙发 Outline 系列，计划为大型开放式办公室内创造出私人区域，以满足当代办公空间不断变化的需求，参与设计的是与 Muuto 长期合作的团队 Anderssen＆Voll。</p><p>设计团队希望为用户提供视觉和声学两个层面的庇护，线条精致优雅，它可以用于独立工作，举行非正式会议，或是休闲放松。这个系列的高靠背沙发提供三座和双座两个版本，轻质木材和钢结构的组合，倒也算轻巧不笨重。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180903194046Jjui3Ze0758hHFMw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180903194046hJvxdLnCWowejB0F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.381980\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180903194045Koy6FnAaPX8OVqHU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.346870\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/08/27/muuto-anderssen-voll-high-back-sofa-outline-furniture-design/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>The three outdoor benches by Studio 7.5 &amp; XtreeE</h3><p>柏林设计团队 Studio 7.5 与巴黎 3D 打印团队 XtreeE 合作，创造了一系列带有编织图案的混凝土长凳。 XtreeE 的六轴 3D 打印机器人，可以极其精确地打印混凝土和粘土。Studio 7.5 曾在之前的项目中使用过其他 3D 打印材料，但他们从未使用过混凝土。</p><p>根据设计师的说法，编织图案是专门为长凳开发的，以前没有使用过。这些长凳是 Studio 7.5 定制街头家具系列的一部分。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180903194134TegY6O4jWQm9cPxG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.658206\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180903194135IAPBkHb81tfDedQv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.658206\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180903194134EvdNf9CtAmKuphM2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180903194136gVHqDw14Xcu3lZy8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.652707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180903194137dHo5DbLKi02QSt3X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.654399\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/08/27/3d-printing-woven-concrete-benches-xtreee-studio-75-design/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Orbit light by Jesse Ede</h3><p>南非艺术家、设计师 Jesse Ede 推出了吊灯 Orbit，灵感来自于月球运行的轨迹。这也是设计师月球主题的第三款作品，之前还有月球桌和长凳。</p><p>Orbit 吊灯由实心黄铜制成，配有一个灯臂和灯泡，可以围绕中心铸铜圆顶 360 度旋转，用户可以选择任何角度照亮空间，点亮内部时灯体会反射出金色的光芒，点亮外部时会发出明亮的蓝光。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=z077584h12t\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180903194216EtCrHYTfbIygiUM9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.735195\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180903194217EAn5dXaqCN468oWb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.436548\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180903194216unkxbcPUGAv91zSl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Lehenga Table by Helen Kontouris </h3><p>墨西哥设计师 Helen Kontouris 设计了一系列名为 Lehenga 的边桌，设计灵感来源于同名的传统印度长裙，设计师精确捕捉到 Garba 舞蹈的优美姿态，并用一款实用的现代家具作品进行诠释。</p><p>这款边桌由不对称锥形底座和圆形网状桌面构成，有两种不同尺寸和五种配色可供选择，桌子采用钢材、钢化玻璃制作，整体搭配亚光面漆。</p><p>正如 Lehenga 长裙的伸缩腰带适合多种不同身材的人们穿着一样，Lehenga 边桌也有着极高的适应性与功能性，可以适用于多种不同的便利场合，用来摆放小物、书本或饮品，室内室外均可使用，十分方便。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180903194259ecBnkYo03bX2Uh8K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706601\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180903194259DjeHxNAUmMYGI9ts.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180903194259GlRptiuZYr0kHSqE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706601\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180903194300ybkOQVeT7ZLX48Ai.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706601\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180903194300dOlvjg6BW4FwDuCE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414425\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180903194301CaOYm2lS1JhFoti6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414425\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>trial and error by Taku Omura</h3><p>品牌 logo 又被设计师玩出了新花样。最近，日本设计师 Taku Omura 便将品牌 logo 通过 3D 打印技术呈现出来，不过，更惊奇的是这些 logo 还具有功能性，成了一件件有趣的居家用品，比如把 Adobe 的 logo 变成了衣架，Louis Vuitton 的 logo 成了收纳篮，Twitter 的小鸟状 logo 成为切橙子利器。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809031943447GBKmPA0LbWlh8J1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.447178\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180903194344kJTrNxKh0v5D9tPA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.681000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180903194344mUPQ4W7pbrloT2Ja.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.651696\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180903194345D1z3UxSaom2IVhHf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.728000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180903194345hR8MZKoVPmx46kiv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.518456\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180903194345NaDdtqrpIoLOmUe3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.204819\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.spoon-tamago.com/2018/08/02/taku-omura-transforms-company-logos-into-3d-printed-items/\" rel=\"nofollow\">spoon-tamago</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>The Iconic Pillow Collection by Throwboy</h3><p>苹果公司这些年推出过不少经典产品，像是 iPhone 4，初代 Macintosh，Apple II 及 iMac 等划时代的产品。最近，一家名为 Throwboy 的公司上线众筹网站 Kickstarter，推出以初代 Macintosh，Apple II，iMac，iPod 和 iPhone 为主题的靠枕产品，早鸟价 39 欧元，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/throwboy/the-iconic-pillow-collection-by-throwboy\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180903194441Gt32IVzLJ9ZDQCEU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180903194441vIWKCT4tA3Yoqlzg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180903194442Sj2FHoCRwhIZ4r1J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180903194442DdGbY2jqyvu8efTP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180903194443vpdOz4s9TAIPqKoR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809031944435uyUKqMbtQlvzgNB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}